==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spheroconic
<hw>Sphe`ro*con"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Geom.)</fld>
<def>A nonplane curve formed by the intersection of the surface of an
oblique cone with the surface of a sphere whose center is at the vertex
of the cone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spherograph</ent>⟦br⟧
